node.text: August is the beginning of the turn towards darkness 🌚☀️🌹It’s almost time to say goodbye to nature’s bounty. By expressing your gratitude for your blessings in a ceremonial way, you invite more to follow. Prepare for the long farewell to summer with me as I read an excerpt from my Book of Blessings and Rituals, available on Amazon and all major bookstores.

node.title: The Book of Blessings & Rituals - A Reading with Athena Perrakis

node.text:
Are you ready to explore your spirituality and step into your full potential? 🦋🌙

Join Soul Shift Alchemize to expand your personal power, deepen your inner wisdom, and manifest joy, prosperity, and confidence. This online program will help you shift your mindset, so you feel more aligned and excited about your life and your future.

Alchemy is a process of transforming one substance, state of being, thought form, or creation into another. Alchemy is the process of becoming YOU – fully, passionately, and unapologetically.

It's never too late to start your healing journey, visit the link in bio to learn more and sign up for Soul Shift Alchemize.

node.text: Ready to dive into the magic of astrology? Save this simple cheat sheet to help you remember key facts about each zodiac sign 💫 🪐  Astrology moves us past the surface-level focus on what we’re doing, to why we’re doing it, and into the deeper need or desire beneath. This type of understanding leads to increased acceptance, compassion, sense of meaning and purpose, and inspiration to evolve. Drop your sun, moon, and rising in the comments!

node.text: It's Prayer Wednesday, a day dedicated to you to your struggles, needs, and desires 💕🙏 Know that someone is listening, and with divine timing, what you pray for today will come to you. Share your prayers below, and if you have none, I invite you to join me in holding space for those who do.

node.text:
Happy Leo New Moon 🌑 🦁 ⠀
⠀
This is the most potent time to initiate new ideas, projects, and all kinds of new beginnings. The dark moon is full of possibility – you don’t need to know how things will unfold, you just need to take action to get it started. This is the time to set intentions based on your deepest desires, release fear, lean into faith, and trust your inner vision. To add to the magic, this New Moon is at the peak of Lion’s Gate, a serious vortex of star power that will empower your intentions.⠀
⠀
I have two online rituals for you today! My FREE online New Moon Ritual starts at 6 pm PT. I also prerecorded a Lion’s Gate Ritual you can watch today at 8 am or 8 pm in your own timezone. Find both links in the bio and stories! ⠀
⠀
✨ Gorgeous photo by @creativewannabe_

node.text:
Lion's Gate reaches its peak tomorrow! 🦁⭐ The Sun and Leo are naturally associated with the Solar Plexus Chakra, the energy center that sits about three inches above the navel and is the seat of your personal power. The Lion’s Gate portal is an invitation to accept and amplify your own power and use it in ever-expanding ways. A balanced Solar Plexus Chakra manifests as self-confidence, healthy self-control, and willpower. It directly correlates to prosperity and the entire cycle of manifestation. If you’ve been struggling with finances, you can use this energy portal to guide your stream of thought in the direction of abundance and tap into the frequency and flow of money and resources.⠀
⠀
Here are some stone recommendations for tomorrow's big event! Don't miss my free online ritual! Link in bio to learn more 💫

node.text:
Activating the Crown Chakra today with my favorite purple stones 💜 👑 ⠀
⠀
The Crown Chakra resonates with wisdom, connection to the spiritual realms, and attunement with the Universe. Activate this energy center to go beyond the personal and immerse yourself completely in the ineffable reality of love, bliss, and pure awareness that is Source.⠀
⠀
To activate your Crown Chakra, compose a prayer or invocation, or choose a mantra that feels resonant with your energy right now. Ask for help, and call on your spirit guides, angels, or ascended masters. If you'd like to learn more about the chakras, follow the link in bio to read my blog. ⠀
⠀
